 |journal=[[The Journal of Clinical Investigation]]
 |volume=83 |pages=1661–1666
 |year=1989
 |doi=10.1172/JCI114065
 |pmid=2708527
}}</ref> Expression of PDGF in particular PDGF-AA is triggered during ocular injury and contributes to PVR pathology.<ref>
